India.

00:07:42.769 --> 00:07:47.642
Prof: Okay,
absolutely, so the forward

00:07:47.642 --> 00:07:54.399
integration of SELCO is its most
obviously unusual feature.

00:07:54.399 --> 00:07:58.706
They're reaching into very
difficult markets to do the

00:07:58.706 --> 00:08:02.524
sales and very awkward places to
do the service,

00:08:02.524 --> 00:08:05.370
which has to go with the sales.
 

00:08:05.370 --> 00:08:11.228
If you look now at--another way
of looking at the backward to

00:08:11.228 --> 00:08:15.565
forward story,
it's--I reproduced what was

00:08:15.565 --> 00:08:20.819
